MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

95-1122. Schialdone v. Schialdone. Trumbull County, No. 93-T-5007.

This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal and as a claimed appeal of right. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal be, and hereby is, granted, effective July 19, 1995.
ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
